This type of movie is made with a graphic engine called Machinima. Shitty graphics, severely limited actions of "actors" (A Star Wars movie I saw made of this had the "actors" running with raised lightsabers the ENTIRE movie, even when they weren't planning to use them), and usually, people making movies with this engine has spent far too little time on the script. I shan't say this is bad, but the limitations of the Machinima engine makes for poor movies IMO.
